<p>æ³›å‹çº¦æŸï¼Œç”¨äºé™åˆ¶æ³›å‹çš„å–å€¼</p>
<p>ä¸ºäº†ç¡®ä¿<code v-pre>nameToUpperCase</code>å‡½æ•°é‡Œçš„å‚æ•°<code v-pre>obj</code>æœ‰<code v-pre>name</code>å±æ€§ï¼Œæˆ‘ä»¬éœ€è¦ä½¿ç”¨<code v-pre>hasNameProperty</code>æ¥å¯¹æ³›å‹è¿›è¡Œçº¦æŸï¼Œä¿éšœè¯¥æ³›å‹ä¸€å®šæ˜¯æœ‰<code v-pre>name</code>å±æ€§</p>
<div class="language-typescript ext-ts line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-typescript"><code><span class="token keyword">interface</span> <span class="token class-name">hasNameProperty</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
